skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: body timer
des: The body timer is designed to be used with 1500W LED Red Light Therapy units. The timer is designed to notify the user when to turn around when doing whole body sessions. To start the timer Say Alexa start Body Timer, and select a timer between 16, 18 or 20 minutes.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
